               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) ʾOrit za-lǝdat “Genesis” (fols. 5ra-42vb), incomplete (the beginning is missing) &#xD;
II) ʾOrit za-ḍaʾat “Exodus“ (fols. 43ra-74va) &#xD;
III) ʾOrit za-lewāwǝyān “Leviticus” (fols. 74vb-100ra) &#xD;
IV) ʾOrit za-ḫʷǝlqʷ “Numbers“ (fols. 100rb-138va) &#xD;
V) ʾOrit za-dāgǝm “Deuteronomy” (fols. 139ra- 170va) &#xD;
VI) ʾOrit za-Yoseʿ “Joshua” (fols. 170vb-194vb) &#xD;
VII) ʾOrit za-masāfǝnt “Judges” (fols. 194vb-216ra) &#xD;
VIII) ʾOrit za-Rut “Ruth” (fols. 216rb-216vb), incomplete (the end missing)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-2.</summary>
                  
                  
