                        <note>In the text on <locus target="#186">186</locus>, there is a gap from Josh. 18:8 to Josh. 18:14. 
                           The missing passage Josh 18:8-14 is found transposed in <locus from="189va" to="190ra">189va-190ra</locus>, in the middle of Josh 21:34. 
                           The error can not be explained by the displacement of the folio, and it is unlikely that it arose during the writing. 
