                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. was probably rebound and resewn. Half of the front board is missing. Leather cover is torn off, only turn-ins are preserved. A few leaves originating from two different Mss. were included in quire I. Most of the fols. are badly damaged by water and fire, esp. in the upper part of the leaves, with loss of some text. Text abraded in <locus from="149v" to="150r">149v-150r</locus>. <locus target="#89">89</locus> (Lev 8:35–10:8) is misplaced (should be between <locus from="80" to="81">80-81</locus>). Gen. 1:1–3:7 and Ruth 2:2–4:22 are missing.</condition>
